    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@tkrugg Like I said in the PR description it was used inside the previous URLSync implementation called `URLSync`. The translation of the URL into `SearchParameters` was attached to this attribute inside the [`URLSync`](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/48a8d66746eb51fc0bc135f38182f84bc92ced37/src/lib/url-sync.js#L115-L119) widget. With the `routing` system this step is performed directly inside the manager with the [`getAllSearchParameters`](getAllSearchParameters) function that is called at the configuration phase. The lifecycle `getConfiguration` is not tied to the URL anymore, it's only one purpose is to create the \"configuration\" (setup the facets, limit, etc...) for the widget.",
